Date: 1999-04-29

Title: Null Branes in Curved Backgrounds

Comments: 19 pages, LaTeX, no figures. Extended version. To appear in Phys.

Rev. DJournal-ref: Phys.Rev. D60 (1999) 125011

We consider null bosonic p-branes in curved space-times. Some exact solutionsof the classical equations of motion and of the constraints for the nullmembrane in general stationary, axially symmetrical, four dimensional, gravitybackground are found.